-- Athi Seeks Bids for Kenya Dam Project, Water Treatment Facility
-- B y   P a u l   R i c h a r d s o n
-- 2013-02-07T12:40:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-07/athi-seeks-bids-for-kenya-dam-project-water-treatment-facility.html
State-owned Athi Water is soliciting
bids to design and build Karimenu II dam near Thika, 41
kilometers (22 miles) north of the capital Nairobi, as well as a
water-treatment plant and transmission pipeline, according to a
statement the water company published in Standard newspaper.  Tenders must be submitted by Feb. 28, Athi said. No other
terms were given.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Paul Richardson in Nairobi at 
 pmrichardson@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Randall Hackley at 
 rhackley@bloomberg.net  